data.title: Wisconsin Intercollegiate Athletic Conference
data.meta_description: As of May 27, 2024, the WIAC has captured 127 National Collegiate Athletic Association (NCAA) Division III team championships. Including championships from NCAA
data.text:
As of May 27, 2024, the WIAC has captured 127 National Collegiate Athletic Association (NCAA) Division III team championships. Including championships from NCAA Division II, NAIA, AIAW, NCGA and NGCA, the conference has collected 188 titles. Following is a complete list of all NCAA and non-NCAA championships won by each school (including former members).
